| `tdd-guard.sh` | PreToolUse (Edit/Write) | Blocks code writing without existing test |
| `auto-test.sh` | PostToolUse (Edit/Write) | Runs related test automatically |
| `tdd-eval.sh` | UserPromptSubmit | Evaluates TDD cycle in user prompt |
{{/ifRule}}
{{#ifRule "feature-planning-gate"}}
| `planning-gate.sh` | PreToolUse (Edit/Write) | Blocks implementation without planning docs |
